{
  "stem": "16.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this, this, this girl, that-- she got into the habit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "One morning, she just brought me a, a small tomato.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I had never eaten a tomato in my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I always hated it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "This one was delicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That was my first tomato in my whole life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And these are the little things that I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I will probably remember other things once you leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't even know what a psychiatrist is, frankly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I mean, what do they do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And slowly, I was made to understand that life must go on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a reason why you were left alive, and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, as I said then, there is my reason.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I would have kept everything inside of myself, I would've just burst from anger, from everything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this, this helped me a great deal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's no question about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I don't remember the specific details.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I do remember that every time I, I left there, I felt better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For some reason, I felt-- I didn't feel so tight inside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I felt better.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, frankly, I was looking forward to my next visit with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and, and I said to myself, this guy's making me feel good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- as a matter of fact, I have-- I have it somewhere, a letter from him that he attended-- he says, you might need it sometime in the future-- that I attended his visits with him, and so on, for a period from this on-- onto that month, and so on and so.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never needed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I bet you, if I go through my old, old papers, I will find it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
